            <p>ii. l. 9,  <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΧΟΝ</foreign> MAMA. The superfluous iota is very lightly cut.</p>
            <p>iii. l. 6-9, <foreign xml:lang="grc">πά<supplied reason="lost">σης διὰ</supplied> παντὸς <supplied reason="lost">εὐκοσμί</supplied>ου δόξ<supplied reason="lost">ῃ διαφέρου</supplied>σαν ἀ<supplied reason="lost">ρετῆς</supplied>
               </foreign> ΜΑΜΑ.</p>
